    public class MaterialRange
extends AbstractValueWidget<Integer>
implements com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.HasChangeHandlers, HasError
    Material Range - a slider that initialize the minimum and maximum values.

    UiBinder Usage:

      <m:MaterialRange value="2" min="20" max="50" value="25"/>
    Author:
    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol
    See Also:
    Material Range
